snippet.title: Temple of the Lizard Men 4 Sneak Preview
snippet.description:
This is a slideshow showcasing my current DOOM project, Temple of the Lizard Men 4. This is the 4th installment in the series and it is done. For further information, check out www.zdoom.org in the forums under "Projects."

TOTLM4 has been released! Here is the link:

https://www.doomworld.com/idgames/levels/doom2/Ports/megawads/lmtmple4

Music Credit:
Capcom & Namco - Street Fighter x Tekken - Credits music and Pandora Theme
